<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card cch">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    
    <hr>
    
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "Profile Image", class: 'profile-img' %>
        
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div 
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_untilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_untilized %>%"
                  ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    
      <div class="col-md-8 about-info">
        <p>I am learning all I can about coding, so that I can become a software engineer. Before I am going to college I will be serving a two year LDS mission.</p>
        <p>After my mission I will be going to Snow College, GO BADGERS!!, where I will participate in the Software Engineering Bachelors Program</p>
        
        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>
          
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>
      
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
                  04/29/15-07/24/17: Key Inshop: Jimmy Johns in Pleasant Grove
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
                  07/24/17-Current: Person in charge: Jimmy Johns in Pleasant Grove
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
                  00/00/00-Current:  : Exit Kryptos
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
                  05/25/17: Pleasant Grove High School, Pleasant Grove, Utah
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
